Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的一集马上就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.37,0:00:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重返人间的亡魂集团七人帮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击了我们藏身的小庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千钧一发之际
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.58,0:00:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶来相救的犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又碰上了新的对手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.78,0:00:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师  珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.92,0:00:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.15,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.42,0:00:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.86,0:00:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.06,0:00:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.27,0:00:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.07,0:00:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.21,0:00:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.42,0:01:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.07,0:01:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.04,0:01:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.81,0:01:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.11,0:01:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.02,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.06,0:01:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.38,0:02:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下  七宝  云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.39,0:02:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.38,0:02:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉\N刚刚放走了你那些伙伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下应该没有后顾之忧了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于醒了是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.05,0:02:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好极了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就安心的在这休养吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.56,0:02:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来这个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.33,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是七人帮的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.61,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样看来\N也无法出动风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.75,0:03:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只好孤注一掷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我乖乖受死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.62,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.66,0:03:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.89,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.06,0:03:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第106话\N戈薇 弥勒 珊瑚命在旦夕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.11,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这味道是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.18,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是尸体跟坟土的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.31,0:04:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道前面还有七人帮吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  应该不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股味道难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你…就是犬夜叉少爷吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.55,0:04:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恭候大驾很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.99,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于追到这里来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.08,0:05:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这座庙的和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.59,0:05:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些村民\N一直都传言得很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.82,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说十几年前\N丧命的那些七人帮亡魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么死后复活了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四处危害这里的村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.23,0:05:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七人帮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.54,0:05:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我埋葬的那些人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.74,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该就是被亡魂烧死的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道只有\N你一个人活了下来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的情况实在太可怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吓得一直躲在\N菩萨后面不敢动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这情形看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.19,0:06:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你也被\N那些七人帮追捕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚  我可要说清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.93,0:06:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是被他们追捕\N是我正在追捕他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.13,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得可不可以告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.63,0:06:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个七人帮\N为什么突然复活了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.07,0:06:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道又能怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.64,0:06:21.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身为菩萨的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着那么多人枉死却无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做点事弥补
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话\N我打算帮那些亡魂超渡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.59,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你\N屈屈一个和尚就能解决的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.03,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这和尚不像是七人帮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他身上还有活人的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.81,0:06:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞低一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.68,0:07:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.92,0:07:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是犬夜叉少爷的\N风之伤留下的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.25,0:07:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉少爷\N大老远跑到北方来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.92,0:07:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真不会是\N为了享受温泉这么简单才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.70,0:07:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞高一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.77,0:07:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快飞高一点呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.71,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.85,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快走就会完蛋的  鸟鸦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我们  钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.59,0:07:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一说到要去找戈薇大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.23,0:07:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢牙少主\N就跑得比飞还要快呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉那股臭味往哪去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…坟土的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.31,0:08:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说一个叫奈落的\N让亡魂死而复活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个奈落\N到底是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.38,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个像妖怪的家伙啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…怎么说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.25,0:08:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他并不是完全的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.62,0:08:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.83,0:08:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早已经逃之夭夭\N不知道躲在哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.26,0:08:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜他一定是\N透过变身的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断在累积自己的能量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.14,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些七人帮\N恐怕只是被他利用的傀儡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是银骨发动的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙难道还没死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚  要命的话\N最好进去躲一躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银骨这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看就要接近真相了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.88,0:09:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.21,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算让我知道\N奈落这家伙根本就信不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几个家伙也可以死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.10,0:09:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.04,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没打够是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又用钢索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住你了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.43,0:09:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭这点玩意儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.33,0:10:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道就妄想…困得住我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.94,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死家伙去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.58,0:10:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会有一股烟味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是七人帮的炼骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.30,0:10:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚刚那个和尚…\N这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.30,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有人的味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛一脸不可置信的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一向\N号称鼻子最灵的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.18,0:10:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么刚刚又会看走眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.81,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.01,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道我身上一点都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七人帮的\N尸体跟坟土的味道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.39,0:10:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.52,0:11:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.69,0:11:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这个地方是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座庙果然抢得很有价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.26,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整座庙四周都是坟墓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.40,0:11:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身上的味道\N当然被盖过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又穿上\N那个活人和尚的袈裟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪你的鼻子实在太灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.34,0:11:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻到这些味道\N马上就放了一百个心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.35,0:11:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这整座庙的和尚\N都已经被你给…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你不是也看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.65,0:11:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经把他们给安葬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才要是能够\N看穿你这点把戏就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股烟是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.19,0:12:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.06,0:12:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.96,0:12:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快起来  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.89,0:12:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我冥加爷爷呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.47,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚闻着师父香炉里的香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.77,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.91,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒法师快起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.61,0:12:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊瑚  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.32,0:12:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都起不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是之前中的毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有毒烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.59,0:12:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一个也别想逃过\N我雾骨大爷的毒烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.10,0:12:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  你振作点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.24,0:13:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身上带着\N四魂之玉碎片的小姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑  七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明给他们吃过解药了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道一点用都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我看先把火灭了再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么办法\N有没有什么办法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.86,0:13:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用震荡陀螺刮起的大风吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐妖术  震荡陀螺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会反效果呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.78,0:13:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.28,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢放火烧庙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.19,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把火可以送他们上西天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他们已经中毒那么深了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.70,0:13:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可以放你进去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混帐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.88,0:14:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚一直有股\N尸体跟坟土的味道传过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是妖狼族的钢牙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有奇怪的家伙出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.10,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是凶骨\N那个笨怪物的同伙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.34,0:14:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们身上的臭味都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.71,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来帮凶骨报仇的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上穿的那条短短的裙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉还真可爱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜\N你不是我喜欢的那一型哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.22,0:14:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那笨蛋在说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.46,0:14:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.93,0:15:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就把你解决掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.37,0:15:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话应该我说才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这把刀到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.07,0:15:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么像蛇一样弯来弯去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.74,0:15:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙啦\N所以你最好乖乖别反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.15,0:15:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我会赶不上\N帮犬夜叉送终啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.62,0:15:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.09,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你刚说这话是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.09,0:15:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么你来不及帮犬夜叉送终
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉是你什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管什么犬夜叉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心的\N是跟着他的那个可爱女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  他们有危险了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好烦  又是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他们早就完蛋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.77,0:15:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么  你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.41,0:15:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母  振作点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个时候受的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上帮你移开柱子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都晕过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家快醒醒  醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.66,0:16:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这个时候我不可以哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要坚强起来才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.47,0:16:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬夜叉回来之前\N我一定要好好保护他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.61,0:16:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  光靠我一个人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本搬不动他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.85,0:17:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动动脑筋\N一定会想出办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就来救你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.49,0:17:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死心吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些同伴全都完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.03,0:17:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是被我放的火烧死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.63,0:17:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是毒发身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你救不了他们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你少废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要坚强起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要坚强起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.95,0:17:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要坚强起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银骨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里面还有法宝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上把你刺穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别做梦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.06,0:18:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没了那把刀  就只有认输啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.34,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妄想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.58,0:18:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子今天没有空陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.81,0:19:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺庙已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.24,0:19:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥勒  珊瑚  戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.42,0:19:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道连杀我的时间都没有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.69,0:19:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢瞧不起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少约略知道\N奈落是什么样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.16,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四魂之玉碎片也弄到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.93,0:19:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.97,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看今天就到此为止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.89,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.49,0:19:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.86,0:20:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人像这小子一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.47,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能一再避开我的蛇骨刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.74,0:20:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个臭小子  倒是有点棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.18,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天本大爷\N没那么多闲功夫陪你玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.25,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再让我看见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的死期了  臭家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我  钢牙少主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.92,0:20:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的毫不犹豫掉头就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.02,0:20:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.77,0:20:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戈薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.98,0:20:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.86,0:21:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬…犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.37,0:21:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.54,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我跟自己说\N一定要坚强起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要坚强起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.48,0:21:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用狐火保护了他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.25,0:21:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家不会被火烧伤对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.32,0:21:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.03,0:21:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明已经尽全力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.47,0:21:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人全都断气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.52,0:22:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.60,0:22:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.07,0:22:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.35,0:22:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.62,0:22:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.16,0:22:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.10,0:23:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.14,0:23:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默默承受伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.91,0:23:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会失去一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.39,0:23:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.93,0:23:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.36,0:23:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人全都断气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.23,0:23:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都要怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.46,0:23:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我早点看穿\N炼骨的谎言就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.20,0:23:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在后悔什么  犬夜叉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.23,0:23:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀生丸
